Description:Test puzzle for replaying an Aura-granted token loop: Squirrel Nest enchants Forest, Earthcraft untaps the Forest by tapping the Squirrel token, and Impact Tremors damages the opponent. Record one cycle that activates the enchanted Forest to create a Squirrel, resolves Impact Tremors, then taps the new Squirrel to Earthcraft targeting the Forest. Repeat until Impact Tremors defeats the opponent.

